"If I'm elected, I'll stop Iran," he said.
“If Obama is re-elected, they will have a bomb.”
He also pledged to increase military assistance to Israel, accusing Obama of failing to keep his promises to that partner.
Entrepreneur Herman Kane, the second candidate in the ranking, has demonstrated discouraging ignorance of the cases.
